# Functional code only

- Prefer pure functions and explicit data flow. No classes unless a framework requires them
  (e.g. FastAPI/Pydantic models, Scrapling `Spider`, React error boundaries).
- No hidden global mutable state; pass dependencies explicitly.
- Small, composable, testable units. Side effects (I/O, network, DB) isolated at the edges.
- Type everything: Python type hints (checked), TS strict mode.
- Comments explain *why* / non-obvious intent — never narrate *what* the code does.
